::Zardus::

Zardus' eyes widen as Feline kisses him, the Alliance commander staring at 
her as she steps back. He realized a mistake he had made. This femm could 
wrap his crew around her little finger! Zardus makes a mental note to talk to 
DevilDuer about making random suggestions. His eyes slide down Feline's body. 
As long as he proggramming functions properly, she would be loyal.

"Um.. Yes, that drink," he says, "We could get it at the mess hall. Follow 
me."

Zardus walks out of the lab, looking back at Feline to make sure she was 
following him.
